title: undefined symbol: GOMP_parallel
body_html:
I get this error when I import torch:

>>> import torch

ImportError: /home/guismay/anaconda2/lib/python2.7/site-packages/torch/lib/libTH.so.1: undefined symbol: GOMP_parallel

But somehow, I don't have it I import numpy before.
